> ;            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> examine khakis
A pair of khaki beige cotton pants. Your khakis contain your kippah and 
your wallet.

> DBG khakis
'khakis' VALUES: | botcover: 16 | 
DONNED: Yes 
IN WORN: Yes 
IN WEARING OF: | hero

